OL,7,FA woman who survived a crossbow attack
OL,8,Fthat killed her partner is calling for
OL,9,Flicensing laws to be introduced on the
OL,10,Fweapon and urging people to respond to
OL,11,Fa new 'call for evidence' from the
OL,12,FHome Office.
OL,14,FLaura Sugden and Shane Gilmer were
OL,15,Fattacked by their neighbour, Anthony
OL,16,FLawrence, in January 2018 when he
OL,17,Fbroke into their home in via the loft
OL,18,Fand shot them both with a crossbow.
