OL,7,FHe attacked the couple after he was
OL,8,Fserved an eviction notice because they
OL,9,Fhad complained about a smell of
OL,10,Fcannabis coming from his home.
OL,12,FMs Sugden, who was pregnant at the
OL,13,Ftime of the attack, was also stabbed
OL,14,Fin the neck at the house in Southburn,
OL,15,Fnear .
OL,17,FShe said that Shane risked his life so
OL,18,Fthat she and their unborn daughter
OL,19,Fcould live.
