OL,7,FThe couple were taken to Hull Royal
OL,8,FInfirmary, but Mr Gilmer, who had
OL,9,Fmanaged to tell 999 operators what
OL,10,Fhappened to him, died on arrival.
OL,12,FLawrence was found dead two days later
OL,13,Fin a lay-by in the North York Moors.
OL,15,F, with the coroner saying that he
OL,16,Fwould write to the Home Secretary
OL,17,Fabout his concerns regarding crossbow
OL,18,Fsales.
