OL,8,Fsaid it was "unbelievable" that the
OL,9,Fsale and ownership of such a "lethal"
OL,10,Fand "medieval" weapon remains
OL,11,Funregulated.
OL,13,F"There are no laws in place to help
OL,14,Fprevent crossbows from falling into
OL,15,Fthe hands of twisted and dangerous
OL,16,Findividuals like Anthony Lawrence,"
OL,17,Fshe said.
