OL,7,FMs Sugden and her legal team launched
OL,8,Fa campaign in 2021 to change the law
OL,9,Faround crossbow sales so that they are
OL,10,Fmore similar to gun ownership laws.
OL,12,FIt gathered more than 42,000
OL,13,Fsignatures, but fell short of the
OL,14,Fthreshold to be considered for debate
OL,15,Fin parliament.
