OL,7,FThe Home Office response at the time
OL,8,Fsaid: "Crossbows are subject to
OL,9,Fstatutory controls. Legislation is
OL,10,Falready in place to deal with those
OL,11,Fwho use crossbows as a weapon. The
OL,12,FGovernment has no plans to legislate
OL,13,Ffurther at this time."
OL,15,FSix years on from the attack, Ms
OL,16,FSugden said she would "probably never"
OL,17,Fmove on from it.
OL,19,F"I still think about it everyday and I
OL,20,Fprobably always will," she said.
