OL,7,FHer daughter Ella, who she was
OL,8,Fpregnant with at the time, is now five
OL,9,Fyears old, but has never known her
OL,10,Ffather.
OL,12,FShe said: "She is very, very, very
OL,13,Fsimilar (to Shane), not just in her
OL,14,Flooks but in her personality, which is
OL,15,Fobviously a huge comfort to me... but
OL,16,Fsometimes that can be hard as well."
