OL,7,FThe pace of change has been
OL,8,Ffrustratingly slow for her, but with
OL,9,Fthe fresh call for evidence from the
OL,10,FHome Office on Wednesday, she is
OL,11,Fhopeful something might be done.
OL,13,F"My opinion would always be that
OL,14,Fpolice control needs to be involved,"
OL,15,Fsaid Ms Sugden.
OL,17,FThe Home Office call for evidence
OL,18,Ffollows a high-profile incident in
OL,19,Fwhich a on Christmas Day in 2021.
