OL,15,Fage of 18 is legally allowed to
OL,16,Fpurchase or possess a crossbow of any
OL,17,Fpower rating, something Ms Sugden says
OL,18,Fis "terrifying" and wants changed to
OL,19,Fintroduce licensing laws similar to
OL,20,Fthose around gun ownership.
